data.description: GREAT LOCATION - GREAT HOME - GREAT PRICE. Close to Cahoon park, Nancy Lopez Golf Course, Cello Grande walking trails & soccer park. 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 baths (nicely remodeled in 2020), ample closets and lots of storage. The kitchen has custom casbinets, pantry and a lovely shadowbox window perfect for a herb pot garden. New Carpet. Beautiful established neighborhood. Large back yard sectioned with garden areas, mature fruit and pecan trees, and extra large gate. Sprinkler system F&B. Large back covered patio with 2 storage rooms.
